Convenient to hang: rustic wood wall signs are easy to install and disassemble, you can directly hang them in many places because quality nails on their back, which can help you to save time and energy; Moreover, you can fix these beautiful signs on the wall or door with flat tacks we provided, not easy to swing or fall

Pretty gifts: the retro vintage home decor is designed with classic quote saying words: I Still Remember The Days I Prayed for What I Have Now, which can make you feel in the church when praying, and make your prayer more pious; It is also a nice gift to give friends, classmates, family, colleagues, etc., for housewarming, birthday, holiday

Solid material: the rustic wood sign is made of quality wood material, safe, light but sturdy, not easy to break, can be applied with your confidence; Adopting nice craftsmanship, the wooden sign has a smooth surface and clear printing, which is reusable and easy to store

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Price was right, quick ship and I am very happy with the item. I love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I was pleasantly surprised!
reviews.reviewText: I read the reviews on this one and many others on Amazon and decided to go with this one. I was pleasantly surprised and I'm keeping it. There were remarks about it being cheap, etc. It is a great value for what I received. I might add something to the edge to make it be a "real border" (it's painted border which I knew from watching the video and reading comments), but it's perfect the way it is. I can sometimes be "extra" so I might add those wooden half beads along the edge since I have those already in my craft collection. I highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars You Get What You Paid For.
reviews.reviewText: What do you expect when considering what you paid for it? If I hadn’t had anything extra decor to go with it, I’d be bothered by how small it is. It is lightweight made out of particle board or some similar material. It’s alright I suppose if you have things to go with it.

reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Cheesy, cheap appearance
reviews.reviewText: The product appears like it is wooden but in fact has a cardstock look when it arrives. Very cheap looking. Definitely not worth the price. No actual frame or any such type of look. I would have been better printing and framing myself.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 15, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Smaller than I expected but that’s my fault for not reading the dimensions. Still cute though!

This is a thin piece of cheap craft wood with a print on it. From the photos, I thought it was going to be framed in real wood.It's a risk to buy a product on Amazon without customer reviews, so I wanted to leave one for others who maybe considering this. I don't hate it, but it does look cheap, and the quality is something you'd find at the Dollar Tree. Like I said, it wasn't what I was expecting, but am going to keep it. I do love what it says.
